  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were not allowed for the Jews to wear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We needed to turn them in to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we didn't turn them all in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So sometimes we used to even buy them off from other people and give it to him, and he took it to Lietsmannstadt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there he exchanged it for some money, and that money enabled some of the other people to buy some food on the black market.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because those children or the people that smuggled it in, they not only smuggled it in for themselves, but they smuggled it in to-- to sell.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I say, thousands die, a few survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's hard to say why the few survived, but it was just luck and maybe resourcefulness or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Circumstances or something that guide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even though they took our business away and everything without any compensation or something, but somehow he was guided we could exchange some goods with him, and he helped us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In turn, we could help somebody else too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this is a-- And I was usually a very thin child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I was a little, I-- I was a very small eater.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, my mother was always afraid that I'm going to get sick, so they used to carry the food around me and-- and stuff me with it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It came to a point that let's see chocolate milk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They forced me to drink it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until after the war, I did not like.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "During-- during the war, if I would've gotten it, I would've loved it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But till the war broke out, I did not like any chocolate milk or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
